                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/3851" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0527</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8394 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">一步错步步错：信用贷款的发放要慎重</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">One mistake leads to another：Credit loan issuance should be cautious</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">孙芳城，肖梦圆，钟廷勇，来先龙</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农行绵竹支行</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">信用贷款；承诺函；信贷风险管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Credit loan; Letter of commitment; Credit risk management</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例讨论的是银行基于对企业做出的不抵押其资产的承诺，向该企业发放信用贷款，但在背后，企业与其关联公司签订《最高额抵押合同》是否有效的问题。东方电气集团旗下的半导体公司专门从事光伏产品的研发、生产、销售，同时，经银监部门批准，集团还设立东气财务公司。光伏产品在前些年风光无限，半导体公司从农业银行绵竹支行获得了5亿元的信用贷款，但承诺在未还清银行信用贷款之前不将财产作为他行贷款的抵押担保。风口过后，产业整体陷入了低谷，半导体公司陷入财务危机，不得不向集团财务公司借款，并签订抵押合同。这就与其之前的承诺相背离，在5亿元信用贷款无法收回的情况下，银行要求确认抵押合同无效。案例引导学生关注银行信贷风险管理相关问题，启发学生对风险管控的思考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case discusses the bank&#39;s commitment to the company&#39;s unsecured assets and the issuance of credit loans to the company, but behind the issue, the company and its affiliates signed the issue of whether the &quot;maximum mortgage contract&quot; is valid. The semiconductor company under the Dongqi Electric Group specializes in the R&amp;D, production and sales of photo voltaic products. At the same time, the Group also established Dongqi Finance Company with the approval of the banking regulatory department. Photovoltaic products have been in the forefront of the past few years. The semiconductor company obtained a credit loan of 500 million yuan from the Agricultural Bank of Mianzhu Branch, but promised not to use the property as a collateral guarantee for other loans before the bank credit loan was paid off. After that, due to the industry fell into a trough, the semiconductor company was in financial crisis, and had to borrow money from the finance company belonging to the same Group, signing a mortgage contract. But it is contrary to its previous commitments. In the case that the 500 million yuan credit loan cannot be withdrawn, the bank asks to confirm that the mortgage contract is invalid. The case guides students to pay attention to issues related to bank credit risk management and inspire students to think about risk management and control.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2013</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《风险管理》、《金融学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">信贷风险管理、风险控制</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
